All Implemented Interfaces:
WrsBindingItem
public class BindingItemAttribute extends BindingItemWithMetaData
This class is container of a wrq:A of binding item in a query. It serves as a marker In WRS-request the Attribute element presents as <Columns> ... <C bRef="column1"> <A name="caption" bRef="column2"/> </C> ... </Columns> See WRS-request XSD for more information about Columns and Attributes rules.
